public class TissueSCell
extends TissueCCell
Extension of TissueCCell for cancerous stem cells.

TissueSCell agents are modified from their superclass:

  • Code change to CODE_S_CELL
  • Cells are immortal (death age set to maximum)
  • Asymmetric division with probability of producing another stem cell (TissueSCell) or a cancerous cell (TissueCCell)
  • No division limit
